00:02:24.920 --> 00:02:27.720
[Amit Varma]: I asked Chuck to be my co-host for the episode.

00:02:27.720 --> 00:02:29.720
[Amit Varma]: And I'm so grateful that Chuck agreed.

00:02:29.720 --> 00:02:33.880
