[Guest]: indie artists,

02:56:52.040 --> 02:56:54.040
[Guest]: Tejas, Komorevi,

02:56:54.040 --> 02:56:56.040
[Guest]: Rohan Rajadaksha,

02:56:56.040 --> 02:56:58.040
[Guest]: Nicholson, Sand Dunes.

